{"id":271569,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-黑龙江癌症患者张淑芝北京上访被拘留（/","date":"2012-12-30T14:46:00Z","modified":"2012-12-30T14:46:00Z","title":"维权网 | 黑龙江癌症患者张淑芝北京上访被拘留（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，黑龙江省绥化市望奎县癌症患者张淑芝到北京控告望奎县驻京办主任姜海军和望奎县公安局长李建伟等人伤害、侵犯其人身财产权的事实，被关押在北京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>马家楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">” </span><span>的黑监狱。次日遭到望奎县公安局雷明晨等人用胶带封住嘴巴，用绳子捆绑双手和双脚强制押送回黑龙江省绥化市望奎县，在公安局审讯室关押十多个小时后又被送到绥化市劳教所。因张淑芝从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年甲状腺癌摘除三个器官，所以劳教所拒收，张淑芝又被送回望奎县遭到十日的行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>关押在望奎县拘留所内。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，张淑芝与前夫徐文俩人病情在当地无法医治的情况下准备一起去北京就医，带着百余张</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B</span><span>超、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CT</span><span>检查报告单和病例卡等，还带着望奎县医院转北京市心脑血管医院的转院证明。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨二点，张淑芝与徐文到达北京站，刚出北京站口，无缘无故被望奎县驻京办主任姜海军等人劫持，对相关转院证明等视而不见，硬说他们到北京上访，强行将两人送往北京大兴区私设的黑监狱，张淑芝在被非法拘禁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>小时内遭到姜海军等人多次殴打，三次昏死过去。姜海军等人还趁机抢走张淑芝的手机、身份证、金手链、金戒指等价值六千多元物品。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>晚，望奎县驻京办主任姜海军和绥化市驻京办李处长带一伙不明身份的人，将张淑芝抬着扔上了北京至青岛</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">T 25</span><span>次列车上逃之夭夭</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">……</span><span>列车出站不久，张淑芝苏醒后发现包内贵重物品都不见了，于是在杨柳青火车站下车返回北京。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日晚</span><span>，望奎县政法委书记王明带着姜海军、李处长（还有五名公安人员：雷明臣、张兴会、王</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">*</span><span>、秦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">*</span><span>、一名女警察）等人，再次将张淑芝押上警车，送绥化市驻京办限制其人身自由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>小时。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>上午九点，绥化市望奎县驻京办主任姜海军拿着手铐进门就说：张淑芝你被逮捕了，就马上把张淑芝按倒在地，带上手铐、并用胶带捆绑双腿。此时女警察从张淑芝身上抢走救命现金四千元，银行卡全抢走（还有姜海军本月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日抢夺张淑芝的物品和现金至今没有归还），并再次将其押上警车，押送人员有上述警察秦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">*</span><span>，还有那位女警察（至今姓名不详）。到达黑龙江省哈尔滨某旅店时是半夜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>点左右，这时张淑芝恳求秦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">*</span><span>给打开手铐休息，他不但不给打开，反而将张淑芝双手背铐，堵上嘴巴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">……</span><span>残忍地折磨，张淑芝多次昏死过去，一直折磨到天亮。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点左右，一行人将身患多种重大疾病的张淑芝送到黑龙江省戒毒劳教所，非法劳动教养一年，但没有任何法律手续，没有任何犯罪事实，无故关押张淑芝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">365</span><span>天！　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>张淑芝在劳教所中每天都让戒毒劳教所提供法律文书，因此戒毒劳教所只得在张淑芝即将出狱时扔给她一份（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>造假</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>《劳动教养决定书》的复印件，绥劳教字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[2006]</span><span>年第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>号，望奎县公安局弄虚作假，大肆作弊欺压百姓，精心策划（用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">06</span><span>年）第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">47</span><span>号聆询告知书代替劳动教养决定书，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>法律文书</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>作枉法处罚张淑芝的依据，虚构事实。（谎称张淑芝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">06</span><span>年在逃至今）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>自从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年以来，原望奎县信访局 长孙立 君多次通知张淑芝说政法委王明给帮助办理生活低保，并在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月办完手续。张淑芝于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月开始找相关领导办理病退，同年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月份办完病退手续，张淑芝因父亲及姐姐患病于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">08</span><span>年相继去逝。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月张淑芝本人因患甲状腺癌在黑龙江省医院手术治疗，在此期间张淑芝还在望奎县北三道街路北租住姓董一间房屋居住，望奎县有关权威人员瞪着眼睛说瞎话，称张淑芝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">06</span><span>年至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">09</span><span>年在逃等谎言，身为国家公务员，竟然徇私枉法，不分青红皂白，欺下瞒上，制造冤假案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>张淑芝于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>号下午上访到公安部信访处，再次遭到黑龙江绥化市望奎县驻京办人员非法关押。望奎县信访副局长王亚文、公安人员：雷明臣、张兴会等人再次把张淑芝送进北京市大兴区鹅房村私设的黑监狱，抢走手机，上访材料</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">U</span><span>盘，撕碎衣服，并且把她交给三个不明身份人暴力殴打。　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>，黑龙江省驻京办朱龙处长等人从黑监狱里解救出张淑芝。朱龙处长责令信访局长魏云平、公安局局长李伟建等人在两个月之内拿出解决方案或作出书面答复意见，两个多月已经过去了，张淑芝仍然至今没有收到任何答复意见，都互相推诿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月，控诉无门的张淑芝向美国大使馆求助，又被望奎县公安局作出行政拘留十日，期满转劳动教养二年的处罚。后因张淑芝病情复发才得到允许外出求医。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张淑芝多年上访无果，由于经常遭到迫害，她的病情恶化，已剩下两个肝叶全病变性占位，已无法救治的严重后果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>维权网一直关注张淑芝的身体健康状况及上访诉求，北京宋庄艺术家追魂大师也非常关心和同情张淑芝的遭遇，今年夏天追魂洗耳恭听张淑芝上访的起因和遭受的迫害之后，眼眶湿润并表示关切之情。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>黑龙江省绥化市望奎县地方政府对一个动过三次大手术，切除三个器官的癌症患者张淑芝，不仅没有尽到救助的责任，还非法侵犯其生命健康权、财产权、信访权、人身自由权，多次对其实施暴力截访、非法关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张淑芝的亲友恳请媒体和社会各界人士关注她的命运，同时也希望有关部门尽快还张淑芝一个公道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张淑芝电话；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13240323220</span></div>\n<p><span>张淑芝的姐姐电话；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13848202328</span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_Z9lIHm69x8/UOBHYco_OFI/AAAAAAAAXyg/YZ1XC6U5xys/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E5%90%91%E8%83%A1%E9%94%A6%E6%B6%9B%E3%80%81%E6%B8%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%9D%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91PICT0158.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-_Z9lIHm69x8/UOBHYco_OFI/AAAAAAAAXyg/YZ1XC6U5xys/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E5%90%91%E8%83%A1%E9%94%A6%E6%B6%9B%E3%80%81%E6%B8%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%9D%E6%B1%82%E6%95%91PICT0158.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-m4m6erMg3Rw/UOBHbMcw-vI/AAAAAAAAXyo/3uCWcBu77rQ/s1600/%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%AE%B6%E8%BF%BD%E9%AD%82%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%B3%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E5%92%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%83%85%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%99%E6%B1%9F%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%EF%BC%88%E5%B7%A6%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E9%81%AD%E9%81%87.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-m4m6erMg3Rw/UOBHbMcw-vI/AAAAAAAAXyo/3uCWcBu77rQ/s320/%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%AE%B6%E8%BF%BD%E9%AD%82%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%88%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%B3%EF%BC%89%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E5%92%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%83%85%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%99%E6%B1%9F%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%EF%BC%88%E5%B7%A6%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E9%81%AD%E9%81%87.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>张淑芝向追魂大师诉说冤情</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-R5jrcPMhpXw/UOBHe3NTeoI/AAAAAAAAXyw/XW_mlxzBPwQ/s1600/%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%A4%84%E7%BD%9A%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-R5jrcPMhpXw/UOBHe3NTeoI/AAAAAAAAXyw/XW_mlxzBPwQ/s320/%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%A4%84%E7%BD%9A%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6.jpg\" width=\"222\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-oSfGapXilL4/UOBHmbeMxZI/AAAAAAAAXy4/tUK4YoGU8jA/s1600/%E8%81%86%E8%AF%A2%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-oSfGapXilL4/UOBHmbeMxZI/AAAAAAAAXy4/tUK4YoGU8jA/s320/%E8%81%86%E8%AF%A2%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%A6.jpg\" width=\"243\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ilMy9_5T3vs/UOBHweB73wI/AAAAAAAAXzA/U-O6bJh0_WQ/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%99%E5%85%BB%E8%AF%81%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ilMy9_5T3vs/UOBHweB73wI/AAAAAAAAXzA/U-O6bJh0_WQ/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E9%99%A4%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E6%95%99%E5%85%BB%E8%AF%81%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%A6.jpg\" width=\"231\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-1U_zWAVrtjU/UOBH28DYfiI/AAAAAAAAXzI/vprfAdWt74o/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%B3%E6%95%99%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A1%B5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-1U_zWAVrtjU/UOBH28DYfiI/AAAAAAAAXzI/vprfAdWt74o/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%B3%E6%95%99%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A1%B5.jpg\" width=\"223\" /></a></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-SGDqxqvFLyM/UOBH9bmOw0I/AAAAAAAAXzQ/Db4RzpG8cJI/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%B3%E6%95%99%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC2%E9%A1%B5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-SGDqxqvFLyM/UOBH9bmOw0I/AAAAAAAAXzQ/Db4RzpG8cJI/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%B3%E6%95%99%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%AC2%E9%A1%B5.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-rjJHCLVYA94/UOBIJ82uXvI/AAAAAAAAXzg/kQ25gwzdSf0/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E5%8E%BB%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A6%86%E9%81%AD%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%99%E6%B1%9F%E6%9C%9B%E5%A5%8E%E5%8E%BF%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E6%8B%98%E7%95%9910%E6%97%A5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-rjJHCLVYA94/UOBIJ82uXvI/AAAAAAAAXzg/kQ25gwzdSf0/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E5%8E%BB%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A6%86%E9%81%AD%E9%BB%91%E9%BE%99%E6%B1%9F%E6%9C%9B%E5%A5%8E%E5%8E%BF%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E6%8B%98%E7%95%9910%E6%97%A5.jpg\" width=\"212\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,17850,20534],"tags":[28519,19196]}